1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

2
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:13,920
(Emperor Xing has passed away.)

3
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,890
(The deposed Crown Prince
Nangong Xuanyu)

4
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,040
(slaughtered the six princes
with swift force)

5
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:19,760
(and purged the traitorous officials)

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,380
(to ascend the throne as Emperor.)

7
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:24,000
(Even though
the Emperor is a ruthless tyrant,)

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,600
(who resembles an Asura,)

9
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:29,160
(noble families still send
their daughters to the capital.)

10
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:31,160
(Yet, to this day)

11
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,360
(no one has won his favor.)

12
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:40,200
(Summon the candidates to the palace!)

13
00:00:44,310 --> 00:00:46,190
(I am the concubine-born
daughter of the Shen family,)

14
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,480
(Shen Zhinian.)

15
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:50,960
(In my past life,
I married the poor scholar Lu Jianglin)

16
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,160
(and helped him
become the Prime Minister.)

17
00:00:53,620 --> 00:00:55,510
(My legitimate elder sister
entered the palace selection)

18
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,050
(but ended up as a discarded consort.)

19
00:00:57,720 --> 00:00:58,880
(In this life,)

20
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,360
(my sister, who once cried
and pleaded to enter the palace)

21
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,800
(actually changed her mind.)

22
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,160
Father, Mother,

23
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:05,510
I'm not going to the palace.

24
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,120
I want to marry Lu Jianglin.

25
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,600
Entering the palace is a dead end.

26
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,000
Let Shen Zhinian go instead.

27
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,680
Shen Zhinian,

28
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,960
you'd better hold onto

29
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,480
this fortune.

30
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,000
This harem

31
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,760
is quite "exciting".

32
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,780
(But she doesn't know)

33
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,880
(that Lu Jianglin)

34
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,240
(is an ungrateful man)

35
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,980
(who killed his own wife
with his own hands.)

36
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,640
(Living this life again,)

37
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:46,160
(rather than helping others to the top,)

38
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,440
(I would rather hold the power myself.)

39
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:51,120
(I will marry the most
powerful man in the world.)

40
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,240
(I'll use him as a stepping stone)

41
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:54,740
(to soar to the highest heights.)

42
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:57,540
=Daughter of Fortune=

43
00:01:57,540 --> 00:01:58,940
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream")

44
00:01:58,940 --> 00:02:00,140
(Author: Lan Jiujiu)

45
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:03,140
=Episode 1=

46
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,640
The flowers you hold

47
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,080
were all chosen by yourselves.

48
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,320
Be sure to hold onto them tightly.

49
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,920
If the flower falls,

50
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,680
(Shen Zhinian)
you are disqualified.

51
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,020
(Concubine-born daughter
of the Shen family in Chizhou)

52
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:19,220
(Xu Baoqin,
daughter of the Xu family army)

53
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:25,500
(Liu Ruyan,
relative of Dowager Consort Liu)

54
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,920
You actually chose a Yulan magnolia.

55
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,640
How unlucky.

56
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,600
Well, I am different.

57
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,760
What I chose

58
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,000
is a Rhododendron.

59
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,880
His Majesty loves vibrant colors.

60
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,440
The Rhododendron is vibrant.

61
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,160
I will be selected.

62
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,040
The Rhododendron "cries blood".

63
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,520
It's an ill omen.

64
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,080
Shen Zhinian,

65
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,840
how dare you curse me!

66
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,920
I am the daughter of a Great General.

67
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,120
What do you think you are?

68
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,600
You two, please stop arguing.

69
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,040
Baoqin is innocent and lively.

70
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:58,360
Sister Zhinian is
exceptionally beautiful.

71
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,600
I'm sure you will
both make it to the end.

72
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,120
Are you trying to say

73
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,400
that I'm not beautiful?

74
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,280
Everyone says

75
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,440
that Shen Zhinian of Chizhou

76
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,360
is the top beauty.

77
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,040
(Liu Ruyan is trying to make me)

78
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,400
(a target for everyone else.)

79
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,600
Drag them all away.

80
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,880
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

81
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:28,200
Please give me another chance,
Your Majesty!

82
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,360
Your Majesty.

83
00:03:29,390 --> 00:03:31,280
The backgrounds of
these candidates are complex.

84
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,600
Duke Zhen,

85
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,600
Duke Ding,

86
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,660
and the Princess Manor

87
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,960
have all planted their people.

88
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:38,560
(Nangong Xuanyu, Emperor of Daliang)

89
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,680
Since they've arranged
everything for me,

90
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,520
let them stand there

91
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,880
until I finish this game of weiqi.

92
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,160
Treating noble daughters
like weiqi pieces

93
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,660
and leaving them out in the sun

94
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,400
might be hard to justify.

95
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,520
Justify?

96
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,520
When they sent these people,

97
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,840
did they ever try to justify it to me?

98
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:01,080
(This isn't about
testing our endurance at all.)

99
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,360
(Why does he have each of us standing)

100
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,560
(in a specific spot?)

101
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:10,240
(He is treating us like weiqi pieces.)

102
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:22,240
(This is a stalemate.)

103
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,920
(No. 1 Beauty of Chizhou?)

104
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,440
(I'm going to turn her into
the No. 1 Cripple of Chizhou.)

105
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:36,000
(He placed us here as discarded pawns.)

106
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,000
(He cannot solve this game.)

107
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,440
(We will be stuck here forever.)

108
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,920
(This is an ancient endgame.)

109
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:44,840
(It's unsolvable.)

110
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,880
(If you want to break the deadlock,)

111
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,000
(there is only one way.)

112
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,960
(Clear the board.)

113
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,160
(Start over.)

114
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,270
Shen Zhinian, what are you doing?

115
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,440
Shen Zhinian,
what do you think you're doing?

116
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,680
Shen Zhinian of Chizhou,

117
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,600
failed.

118
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,320
Take her away.

119
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,320
(She actually saw the solution.)

120
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,520
(Interesting.)

121
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:08,400
This is the Emperor's
Golden Feather Arrow for the selection.

122
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,900
Why did he choose her of all people?

123
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,680
By imperial decree,

124
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:16,000
Shen Zhinian of Chizhou

125
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,480
is titled Senior Attendant Rou.

126
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,880
She is granted
residence in Tinglan Palace.

127
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:23,280
- Congratulations, Senior Attendant Rou.
- Congratulations, Senior Attendant Rou.

128
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,520
I thank His Majesty.

129
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,560
(I gambled correctly.)

130
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,080
(Receiving a title
so unexpectedly today)

131
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:34,760
(will surely incite jealousy
among the other candidates.)

132
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,680
(From now on, in the palace,)

133
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:38,100
(I must be even more careful.)

134
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:39,260
(Cold Palace)

135
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:44,080
Please bear it a moment longer,
Your Majesty.

136
00:05:44,090 --> 00:05:45,890
The White Snake
treatment is almost finished.

137
00:05:46,610 --> 00:05:47,520
However, Your Majesty,

138
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:49,470
the backlash of the poison
is becoming more dangerous.

139
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,520
If this continues,
the consequences will be bad.

140
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,440
Manshu Tears.

141
00:05:55,010 --> 00:05:56,680
Flowers bloom,
but leaves never see them.

142
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,960
Like entering a realm of ice and fire.

143
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,600
First ice, then fire.

144
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,720
It flares up once a month.

145
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:05,200
I actually quite like it.

146
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:09,160
It's thanks to Dowager Concubine Qin,

147
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,560
who built this secret room
for your treatment

148
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,600
here in the Cold Palace.

149
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,160
Otherwise, every full moon
when the poison flares up,

150
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,400
(Wen Ling, Imperial Guard)
the Duke Zhen would notice something.

151
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,080
Focus on the main task.

152
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:21,280
The matter regarding
the Chifeng Army token

153
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,880
must be handled quickly.

154
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,560
Understood, Your Majesty.

155
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,160
Shen Zhinian of Chizhou

156
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,000
could solve a stalemate.

157
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,520
Interesting.

158
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:39,280
(Tinglan Palace)

159
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:39,920
Young Lady,

160
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,120
I've made inquiries.

161
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,150
There is indeed a eunuch
named Li Congshan in the Cold Palace.

162
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,200
(Handan, Shen Zhinian's Maid)
He is on duty tonight.

163
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,800
As long as he exists, it's fine.

164
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,280
Bring me my cloak.

165
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,580
I'm going to the Cold Palace.

166
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,600
Young Lady, why are you looking for him?

167
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,990
His Majesty hasn't visited
the harem for a long time.

168
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,210
If I want to win his favor,

169
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,440
I must find another way.

170
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,400
Li Congshan used to be the Emperor's
personal attendant.

171
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,960
Because he offended a favored consort,

172
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:04,100
he was banished to work
in the Cold Palace.

173
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,720
He knows a lot about
the Emperor's preferences in bed.

174
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,400
I'm going to consult him.

175
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,680
Preferences in bed?

176
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,660
There are as many as 30 beauties
entering the palace this time.

177
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,360
Yet he only gave me a title.

178
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,600
I don't know what he sees in me.

179
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,560
He might summon me to serve at any time.

180
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,240
I must make sure

181
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:24,230
he remembers me vividly
from the very first night.

182
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,760
Young Lady, how did you become so bold?

183
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,440
Only the bold can carve out a future.

184
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,880
People don't always get
a second chance to start over.

185
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,680
Whitey,

186
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,600
help cover for me.

187
00:07:34,610 --> 00:07:36,680
Then, remember to take
the east side gate, Young Lady.

188
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,900
The area is unguarded.

189
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:40,020
(Cold Palace)

190
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,440
Go ahead.

191
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,440
(How is there no one
in the Cold Palace?)

192
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:21,000
Didn't they say the concubines

193
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,520
sent here were too many to fit?

194
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,160
Whitey.

195
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,000
Whitey,

196
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,240
don't run off.

197
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,680
Careful, or you'll be stewed.

198
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,320
You are...

199
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,120
Who are you?

200
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:51,400
What are you doing here?

201
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,280
I'm looking for my cat.

202
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,480
I mean no harm.

203
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,200
Really.

204
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:06,460
(Attendant)

205
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,120
Are you...

206
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,400
Are you Attendant Li?

207
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,880
Why are you looking for him?

208
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,520
Actually, I came to find Attendant Li

209
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,440
to buy something.

210
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,640
I'm willing to pay handsomely.

211
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,720
Buy what?

212
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,920
The art of seduction.

213
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,080
I wonder

214
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,840
where you plan

215
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,600
to use this art.

216
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:38,700
No need to ask questions, Attendant Li.

217
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,000
Just name your price.

218
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,720
Since you've found me,

219
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,880
you must follow my rules.

220
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,560
What rules?

221
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,280
The rule of inspection.

222
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,280
(Inspection?)

223
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,360
I must check

224
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,960
if your hands are soft enough.

225
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,960
(No internal power.)

226
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,120
I also must check

227
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,680
if your waist is flexible enough.

228
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,560
(No hidden weapons.)

229
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,500
Are you done with your inspection?

230
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,920
It's my turn to inspect you.

231
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,280
Shen Zhinian,

232
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,720
it's been so long.

233
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,400
Is the Emperor's portrait restored?

234
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:33,520
Bring it here quickly.

235
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:42,780
♪Falling at first sight,
a life of turmoil wasted♪

236
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:50,140
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

237
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,440
(Nangong Xuanyu?)

238
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:56,460
♪All the spring colors
lean toward one person♪

239
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:59,200
You seem quite curious
about my appearance, Young Lady.

240
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,400
(Rumor says Nangong Xuanyu
killed his father and brothers.)

241
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,720
(He is prone to distrust.)

242
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,480
(I can't let him realize)

243
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,640
(that I've recognized him.)

244
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:10,120
Attendant Li,
you won't even show your true face.

245
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,240
I'm not doing

246
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:12,360
this deal anymore.

247
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,440
Let go of me.

248
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,160
Madam,

249
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,040
this way.

250
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,200
What should you do?

251
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,240
You can't get away now, can you?

252
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:40,170
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

253
00:11:41,910 --> 00:11:47,140
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

254
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:51,140
♪If we don't meet♪

255
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:54,580
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

256
00:11:54,770 --> 00:12:01,320
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

257
00:12:01,650 --> 00:12:08,100
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

258
00:12:08,450 --> 00:12:14,770
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

259
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:21,980
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

260
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:28,860
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

261
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:34,980
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

262
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:42,510
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

263
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:49,350
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

264
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:56,050
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

